• Able to structure a large project into manageable parts / deliverables
• Ability to manage the aspect of the product assigned with minimal supervision
• Ability to manage members of the product team, including stakeholders
• Able to create and implement a risk management plan for the team
• Able to estimate and communicate progress and deadlines 
• Understanding of Agile methodology (Scrum and Kanban)
• Able to use a project management tool to create, assign and track task (Trello, Jira, e.t.c)
